Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
168 Pacific Highway, North Sydney is perfect for those companies seeking a commercial office which has that little more 'x factor'.  This Victorian terrace is very well presented has polished floor boards, freshly painted walls, high ceilings and good natural light.  All the things which you are looking for if you want to create your own identity for your business and don't want to get caught up in one of the typical office buildings in North Sydney.  This terrace is located a short walk from buzz of North Sydney.

There are also 4 car parking spaces at the rear of the building to lease with this terrace.

Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Base of an 18 Storey Office Tower

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Located on one of the busiest strips of North Sydney, on the corner of Walker & Mount Street, this prime retail opportunity is available now.

- 73.5sqm*
- 18 storey commercial tower, 98.5% occupancy
- Floor to ceiling glass frontage facing Walker Street, in between two busy cafes
- Shared amenities
- Neighbouring retailers include JB Hi-Fi, Aldi Supermarket, Coles Supermarket, Priceline Pharmacy, Commonwealth Bank, ANZ, St George, Suncorp, BOQ & Oporto
- 150m* to Greenwood and North Sydney Train Station
- Metres from the 100 Mount Street development (35 storey tower, completion circa 2019) and a block from the 1 Denison development (36 storey tower, completion circa 2020)
- Currently trading as an optometrist, the property would suit retail, services or medical use
- Proposed extension of shopfronts to be in line with columns

For further details or to arrange an inspection, please contact Amy Pfeiffer 0401 198 401, amy.pfeiffer@cbre.com.au

*Approx.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: PRIME NORTH SYDNEY RETAIL, NEXT TO ALDI AND OPPOSITE COLES

Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Huge Exclusive Use Balcony at the Rear

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Perfectly located in between Pacific Highway and Miller Street, 51 Berry Street has recently undergone an extensive refurbishment of both the ground floor and upper levels.

This prime retail offering can be leased in one line or divided into two tenancies.

- 50sqm* - 387.3sqm*
- North facing, 9m* wide, floor to ceiling glass frontage
- 100sqm* exclusive use balcony located at the rear
- Access to grease & exhaust extraction
- Air conditioning
- Cold shell ready for fit out
- Abundance of natural light with windows throughout the tenancy
- Parking available upon request
- Located at the base of a six storey commercial tower
- Adjacent to the new 30 storey Vodafone building and less than 100m* to the upcoming Metro Line Train Station
- Easily accessible via bus or train

Surrounded by commercial office towers, residential high rises, retailers and schools, the premises would suit F&B, medical, fitness, office or showroom (STCA).  

With an additional 168,000sqm* of office space due for completion by 2021, and major companies such as Channel 9 and Sony relocating to North Sydney, the area is quickly cementing itself as a thriving CBD with prime retail locations. 

For further details or to arrange an inspection, please call Amy Pfeiffer 0401 198 401 or Leif Olson 0409 748 136. 

*Approx.
